"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Iran has threatened to target Qatar's Ras Laffan refinery after an attack on its South Pars gas field. Lawmakers are questioning intelligence officials about the potential threat from Iran.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran Threatens Qatar\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ir\u00e1n ha amenazado con atacar la refiner\u00eda Ras Laffan de Qatar despu\u00e9s de un ataque en su campo de gas South Pars. Los legisladores est\u00e1n preguntando a los oficiales de inteligencia sobre la amenaza de Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ir\u00e1n amenaza a Qatar\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel announced it had killed Khatib, and this was confirmed by Iranian President Masoud Pezeshkian. This event has increased tensions in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel Kills Khatib\",            \"translated_version\": \"Israel anunci\u00f3 que mat\u00f3 a Khatib, y esto fue confirmado por el presidente iran\u00ed Masoud Pezeshkian. Este evento ha aumentado las tensiones en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Israel mata a Khatib\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The USS Gerald R Ford has been important in US military actions during the conflict with Iran. It has been a key part of the operations.\",            \"english_title\": \"USS Gerald R Ford's Role\",            \"translated_version\": \"El USS Gerald R Ford ha sido importante en las acciones militares de EE.UU. durante el conflicto con Ir\u00e1n. Ha sido una parte clave de las operaciones.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Papel del USS Gerald R Ford\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The health ministry reports that 968 people, including over 100 children, have died since March 2. This highlights the ongoing crisis.\",            \"english_title\": \"Health Crisis Report\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ministerio de salud informa que 968 personas, incluyendo m\u00e1s de 100 ni\u00f1os, han muerto desde el 2 de marzo. Esto resalta la crisis en curso.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Informe de crisis de salud\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US central bank is being careful about changing interest rates, even though the president is pushing for a cut. This shows the bank's cautious approach.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Bank Cautious on Rates\",            \"translated_version\": \"El banco central de EE.UU. est\u00e1 siendo cuidadoso con cambiar las tasas de inter\u00e9s, aunque el presidente est\u00e1 presionando para bajarlas. Esto muestra el enfoque cuidadoso del banco.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Banco de EE.UU. cuidadoso con tasas\"        }    ]}"